### Citation Format (Increases Visibility by 40%)

‚ùå **Wrong**: "Studies show this increases conversion"

‚úÖ **Right**: "[HubSpot's 2024 study](url) of 1,000 businesses found this increases conversion by 34%"

**Citation requirements:**
- Specific source name
- Recent date (within 2 years)
- Exact numbers
- Clear attribution with link

